  "image_url": "https://cdn.kirtansewa.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/22005044/Slide3-2.jpg",
  "body": [
    "Bhai Mohinderjeet Singh is among the leading contemporary Kirtanis that continues to serve the Sangat around the world with his mesmerising Kirtan. He is based in Delhi but has traveled extensively for decades. He has accompanied Bhai Rajinder Singh Ji to Singapore, Malaysia and Thailand in the 1980s. Having spent a long time with Bhai Rajinder Singh Ji, he knows most of Bhai Sahib’s compositions and continues to delight the Sangat with those tunes. Besides that, he also accompanied Prof. Devinder Singh Ji. Since he formed his own jatha, he has made many trips to Thailand, Malaysia and Singapore. Most of the recordings below are from these tours. We have only put up the live recordings and not his studio albums. If anyone has more recordings of Bhai Mohinderjeet Singh Ji to share, please contact us."
